## 🗃️ Database Structure

### `EMPLOYEE`
| Field       | Type         | Description       |
|-------------|--------------|-------------------|
| employee_id | MEDIUMINT PK | Auto-increment ID |
| first_name  | VARCHAR(40)  | First name        |
| last_name   | VARCHAR(40)  | Last name         |
| email       | VARCHAR(40)  | Email address     |
| phone       | VARCHAR(40)  | Phone number      |

### `PROJECT`
| Field       | Type         | Description            |
|-------------|--------------|------------------------|
| project_id  | MEDIUMINT PK | Project identifier     |
| deadline    | VARCHAR(40)  | Deadline (as string)   |
| employee_id | MEDIUMINT FK | Links to EMPLOYEE table |

